<Layout title="2032 Olympics 2026 Update: What Brisbane Inner East Property Owners Need to Know | Daniel Gierach" description="The latest 2026 infrastructure decisions on the Brisbane 2032 Olympics, and what they mean for inner east property values, sellers and investors." schema={faqSchema}>

